metadata.description:
Guaranteed access to one exclusive drop.
For a whole year.
That's 12 months.
52 weeks.
365 days.
No joke.

Period of use begins 25 May 2023 and ends 24 May 2024. After this date, this Golden Ticket will not be valid. Learn more at [collect.adidas.com](https://collect.adidas.com). Read the [terms and conditions](https://adidasapp.adidas.com/collect/tc.html).
